Instalar (UBUNTU):

sudo apt-get install python3

sudo apt-get install libpq-dev python-dev libxml2-dev libxslt1-dev zlib1g-dev libldap2-dev libsasl2-dev libffi-dev

sudo apt-get install build-essential

sudo apt-get install python-pip


Dentro do diretorio do projeto, instalar os requerimentos utilizando:

sudo pip install -r requirements.txt
